data.description: Welcome to this meticulously maintained 1-story home nestled in a mature subdivision, in a prime location with seamless access to hwy 75 and 121. Convenience meets comfort, just minutes away from shopping, parks, and all amenities you desire! 4 spacious bedrooms providing ample space. Tall ceilings throughout the home. Enjoy the luxury of 3 full-size bathrooms, including an updated master shower. 2 generous living areas, allowing for flexible use and entertainment options. Dine in style in both the formal dining area and the kitchen dining space. The gourmet kitchen is a chef's dream, featuring abundant storage, and a convenient desk area. Immaculate landscaping surrounds the property, offering stunning curb appeal that welcomes you home. A beautiful privacy fence encases the property, providing a sense of security and seclusion. Step into a peaceful and relaxing backyard featuring a firepit area and chicken coop. Don't miss your chance to call this home!
